{"lemma":"حَتْمُ","slug":"حَتْمُ","root":"ح.ت.م","root_slug":"ح-ت-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ت-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حَتْم","root":"حتم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7063"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%AA%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7063","headword_ar":"حَتْمٌ","root":"Htm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of 1: when used as a simple subst.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A decree, an ordinance, a sentence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a judicial decision;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) accord. to some,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adapted to a particular case:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HutuwmN","text_ar":"حُتُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) It is said in the Kur [xix. 72],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna EalaY rab~ika HatomFA","text_ar":"كَانَ عَلَى رَبِّكَ حَتْمًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqoDiy~FA","text_ar":"مَقْضِيًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is"},{"kind":"text","text":"imposed by Himself"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon thy Lord"},{"kind":"text","text":"as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a decree judicially decided"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And Umeiyeh Ibn-Abi-s-Salt says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"EibaAduka yuxoTiy^uwna waA^anota rab~N\n                      \n                     \n                        bikaf~ayoka AlmanaAyaA wAlHutuwmu"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thy servants sin: and Thou art a Lord: in thy hands are the decrees and the judicial decisions"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b2-  [As a term of the law, it is sometimes used instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaA='N","text_ar":"قَضَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adaA='N","text_ar":"اَدَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  Also [an inf. n. used as an epithet, signifying]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Necessary, requisite,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unavoidable; that must inevitably be done"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suffered"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indissoluble and irreversible:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaA='N HatomN","text_ar":"قَضَا=ءٌ حَتْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an indissoluble and irreversible decree"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordinance"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sentence"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judicial decision"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jzm","text_ar":"جزم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pure; free from admixture; genuine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"formed by transposition from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHotN","text_ar":"مَحْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa AlA^axu AlHatomu","text_ar":"هُوَ الاَخُ الحَتْمُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the pure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"genuine, true, brother."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]}}